snippet.title: Playing Every Apple II Floppy, E168 | Conquering Worlds
snippet.description:
Taking a quick look at Conquering Worlds, a 1983 release for the Apple II.

This is episode 168 of Woz A Day, my series where I'm taking a look at Apple II software in the "WOZ" disk image format uploaded to the Internet Archive "Woz A Day" collection in upload order: https://archive.org/details/wozaday
These are preservation-quality unmodified/uncracked disk images that can pass copy-protection checks and preserve the original "retail" experience.

📋 Woz A Day Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXVtlqgyC7v2ACowTpMXcMrLbfX1qdBHE
💾 Download disk image or play in-browser: https://archive.org/details/wozaday_Conquering_Worlds
Commentary-free version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=snB3TVxKQzI
